{"tid":1397881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣呼籲85全民三罷","createTime":"2019-08-02T15:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:11:52.000Z","uid":279063,"like":118,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"67a32b98c2d8e6b8d2c54e0202eb6ba554861a24","tid":1397881,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"民陣就坊間發起的全民三罷之聲明。<br />\n<br />\n民陣今晚經大會商討後，作出以下聲明。<br />\n<br />\n香港社會堅持五大訴求至今，已近兩個月，經歷數以百萬計的市民參與抗爭，超過二十場大大小小遊行、集會以及其他各式各樣的抗爭，而林鄭政府至今仍置若罔聞，甚至近日以暴動罪等嚴刑峻法政治檢控抗爭者，另一邊廂，元朗恐襲的施暴者卻從未進入司法程序開展檢控，民陣與全香港人同感憤怒，認為和理非的運動抗爭必須進入另一個新的境地，以顯香港人對抗極權的意志。<br />\n<br />\n1. 民陣呼籲香港各界，配合民間的呼籲，在八月五日星期一，發起全民三罷，對抗極權，堅持五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n2. 民陣在此，特別呼籲商界在八月五日當日，容讓僱員就香港的重大前途作出罷工，甚至在可行的情況下以罷市方式，共同守護香港。<br />\n<br />\n3. 民陣在此將會配合坊間各界，而我等亦知悉七區集會的不反對通知書正在申請階段，待各方有進一步消息後，我們將會配合宣傳及動員等等的工作。<br />\n<br />\n4. 由於呼籲三罷屬重大決定，民陣必須正式在大會上作出商討並通過，因此需到此刻才能作出正式呼籲，還請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n5. 民陣將會與社會各界並肩，繼續堅持五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019年8月2日<br />\n<br />\nPhoto: HK01<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Thzkki3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThzkki3.jpg&h=50e41d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/2390084131038964/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F511608535553209%2Fposts%2F2390084131038964%2F&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzYR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=32a82811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/2390084131038964/</a>"},{"pid":"2a1644a7a3bdbb0dd1ed6bc0449c3c0d6b9a07d5","tid":1397881,"uid":236472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a34d5eaa20467cc8ec044c1aa00fb52c180fdc","tid":1397881,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:30:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fdaca7a3cf50e50a0324bf563bda713439753406","tid":1397881,"uid":282031,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"遲到總好過冇到"},{"pid":"79b1ff1b73020dc979226e672b21f9a272e29c6e","tid":1397881,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"三罷民調快d做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又係 yahoo 投票"},{"pid":"a0ba8214d20b17f15d05b9aac1dae6a0aa936890","tid":1397881,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"三罷民調快d做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又係 yahoo 投票"},{"pid":"16222cec78ce99117d953907947121f609ad3f73","tid":1397881,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"496161ce1fa8d82d4077191c38ab181d1fd5978c","tid":1397881,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6826c76067b5aeda532bcebfe87e877447430fee","tid":1397881,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"三罷民調快d做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又係 yahoo 投票"},{"pid":"9c2261bd33cf59dfb1a731b756ec49e83a043f60","tid":1397881,"uid":271407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6054c46c2e8dc94a8012e5faf0f7a4eb37ae454d","tid":1397881,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:33:39.000Z","msg":"85三罷去集會"},{"pid":"205ef2acdafebd002d3d47afc48db2b601340e78","tid":1397881,"uid":261885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理非出黎吧"},{"pid":"dc383df097fffa47778120307fc80ed423560e27","tid":1397881,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc26221bcff53ea6e1bb83d6072e495c6c74c98","tid":1397881,"uid":261986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:35:48.000Z","msg":"(越諗越唔掂) 最快一年內，香港人這概念會被剷除。一場社會文化改造，正在發生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396835</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6791eb45b1ea802543f8ef3d32184097f2baf62b","tid":1397881,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:39:25.000Z","msg":"三罷民調快d做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又係 yahoo 投票"},{"pid":"41906765f7eb17028b717ada86221c1a927ec333","tid":1397881,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/02/4RBCkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F02%2F4RBCkY.jpg&h=81e0817a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e70e9b7a5a1e3c287ad6457efc574c4d424277d5","tid":1397881,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"b3cb439b12818ae087d64652960df4253855cb69","tid":1397881,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"三罷係邊三罷"},{"pid":"4ef13837f59ecd18ace82a724613366f25f380fa","tid":1397881,"uid":66178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9146b27546c6675bb2441a26a03ba1fd2bce8b","tid":1397881,"uid":199126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3cb439b12818ae087d64652960df4253855cb69","tid":1397881,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"三罷係邊三罷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"罷工、課、股市"},{"pid":"6a9faeec055ab4a41c89a8f7a9ef4e86785c7439","tid":1397881,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:45:28.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"434427a1d7142dfd7d753e833fb1e4922ef0dfdc","tid":1397881,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8751e60c274076578774cbfc2af798c90bc8b56","tid":1397881,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82602f5aa51dcd67a28037c992e9f66990fea23a","tid":1397881,"uid":33734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rNJ2KF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rNJ2KF.jpg&h=ee845325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇幾多次都覺得張相好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284f440e0929bc97ef9563a482be0828124ad76c","tid":1397881,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭嚇到標尿未"}]}